    <h2 class="sec-h"><span class="te-content">HIPEC vs PIPAC — <em>తేడా ఏమిటి</em></span><span class="en-content">HIPEC vs PIPAC — <em>What is the difference</em></span></h2>
    <div class="proc-list">
      <div class="proc-item"><div class="proc-tier">T1</div><div class="proc-body"><h4>CRS + HIPEC</h4><p><span class="te-content">Open surgery. All visible tumour surgically remove చేసిన తరువాత, heated chemo abdomen లో circulate. Best candidates: PCI score 20 కంటే తక్కువ, good performance status, resectable disease. 8-12 hour procedure.</span><span class="en-content">Open surgery. After all visible tumour is surgically removed, heated chemo is circulated in the abdomen. Best candidates: PCI score below 20, good performance status, resectable disease. 8-12 hour procedure.</span></p><div class="proc-meta">Sugarbaker Technique · PRODIGE 7 · OVHIPEC · ESSO Hannover Training</div></div></div>
      <div class="proc-item"><div class="proc-tier">T1</div><div class="proc-body"><h4>PIPAC</h4><p><span class="te-content">Pressurised Intraperitoneal Aerosol Chemotherapy. Laparoscopic, minimally invasive. Open CRS+HIPEC candidates కానివాళ్ళకి. 6 weeks కి repeat చేయవచ్చు. Disease control అవుతుంది. Bridge therapy గా use చేయవచ్చు.</span><span class="en-content">Pressurised Intraperitoneal Aerosol Chemotherapy. Laparoscopic and minimally invasive. For patients not suitable for open CRS+HIPEC. Can be repeated every 6 weeks. Achieves disease control and can be used as bridge therapy.</span></p><div class="proc-meta">Hannover Fellowship Training · Repeatable Procedure</div></div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
